    <item>
      <title>经过数月的威胁，特朗普软化了阻止向古巴提供石油的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-threats-oil-cuba-sanctions.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫新闻秘书表示，在一艘满载原油的俄罗斯油轮抵达古巴后，美国将“根据具体情况”评估运往古巴的石油运输情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-threats-oil-cuba-sanctions.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 00:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥就其公民在 ICE 拘留期间死亡向美国施压</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/mexico-ice-detention-deaths.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 表示，墨西哥将采取法律措施，要求改善移民拘留设施的条件。她表示，自特朗普总统上任以来，那里已有 14 名墨西哥公民死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/mexico-ice-detention-deaths.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 00:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
